<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; line-height:1.6; color:#222;">
    <h2>Verify your Saka360 account</h2>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thanks for signing up. Please verify your account by clicking the button below:</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{verification_link}}" style="background:#0ea5e9;color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">
        Verify Account
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>If the button doesn’t work, paste this link in your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="{{verification_link}}">{{verification_link}}</a></p>
    <p>— Saka360 Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
